    "description": "Dive into the mysterious world of <strong>Tricky Castle</strong>, where secrets and unexpected traps lurk at every turn, and help a brave knight rescue the princess.<br><br>In this world, nothing is as simple as it seems. Secrets and traps can catch you off guard at any corner, and every element of the game, even the interface, could be part of a puzzle. Explore mysterious locations, solve unconventional challenges, and overcome numerous trials.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151850/extras/c513f47ae00d5421df1653a8f3f1b997.poster.avif?t=1743329337\" width=630 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151850/extras/c513f47ae00d5421df1653a8f3f1b997.webm?t=1743329337\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151850/extras/c513f47ae00d5421df1653a8f3f1b997.mp4?t=1743329337\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151850/extras/4d1f8d394cc4f4b3997de7cde65f1ebd.webp?t=1743329337\" width=630 height=32 /></span><br>Bright and minimalist graphics enhance the atmosphere of the enigmatic castle, where every detail matters. <strong>Tricky Castle</strong> is a game that will make you wonder and smile at every step.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features:</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>4 unique chapters:</strong> Explore the Castle, the Witch's Tower, the Starry Sky, and the Cave, each filled with secrets and unusual challenges.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Over 170 levels:</strong> Each chapter offers dozens of unique puzzles and hidden locations.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Unconventional puzzles:</strong> The game mechanics challenge your usual way of thinking, pushing you to find solutions beyond the obvious.</li></ul> <ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Secrets and collectibles:</strong> Find hidden stars, bats, and magic puzzles to unlock new levels and opportunities.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Ghost form:</strong> Unlock new abilities to explore the castle from new perspectives.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151850/extras/de69d84599de703bf8dc73dbd0a440d8.poster.avif?t=1743329337\" width=630 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151850/extras/de69d84599de703bf8dc73dbd0a440d8.webm?t=1743329337\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151850/extras/de69d84599de703bf8dc73dbd0a440d8.mp4?t=1743329337\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151850/extras/998ce8eed5bf8cff442aeb883cc1ea9a.poster.avif?t=1743329337\" width=630 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151850/extras/998ce8eed5bf8cff442aeb883cc1ea9a.webm?t=1743329337\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151850/extras/998ce8eed5bf8cff442aeb883cc1ea9a.mp4?t=1743329337\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151850/extras/4d1f8d394cc4f4b3997de7cde65f1ebd.webp?t=1743329337\" width=630 height=32 /></span><br><strong>Are you ready to take on the challenge and rescue the princess?</strong>",
